rows.label: qst200909_0040
rows.name:
They seem to understand just fine.
We might be able to negotiate at this rate.

rows.label: qst200909_0050
rows.name:
We did not come here to fight you.
We came to talk with you.

rows.label: qst200909_0060
rows.name:
We have heard that a man from Trigo
has been brought to this location.

rows.label: qst200909_0080
rows.name:
We not sure if true or nots, but
we katch strange man, yeah.

rows.label: qst200909_0100
rows.name:
Well then, would you be so
kind as to let him go?

rows.label: qst200909_0110
rows.name: Skraaaw! No! We not let him go!

rows.label: qst200909_0120
rows.name: Is there anything we could do to change your mind?

rows.label: qst200909_0150
rows.name: Oh dear. That puts us at an impasse, then.

rows.label: qst200909_0160
rows.name:
Our negotiations are going downhill,
like this weather...

rows.label: qst200909_0170
rows.name:
Oh well! I guess I'll just have to lean on them a little harder.
It would be amazing if we could avoid starting a fight...
